-- IHH Healthcare to buy India's Fortis Healthcare's Singapore unit for $108.5 mln
-- By Yantoultra Ngui
-- Fri Sep 12, 2014 07:08AM EDT
-- None



KUALA LUMPUR, Sept 12 (Reuters) - Malaysia's IHH Healthcare Bhd <IHHH.KL>, Asia's largest hospital operator by stock market value, said on Friday it is buying India's Fortis Healthcare Ltd's <FOHE.NS> Singaporean diagnostic and molecular imaging unit Radlink-Asia Ptd Ltd for 346.53 million ringgit ($108.5 million).

